The data are available by county, county subdivision, place within county, tract/block numbering area (bna), blockgroup, and block. This portion of the ACRP is produced by the Center for International Earth Science Information Network (CIESIN).</Description><DOI><DOI>10.7927/H4Z60KZ9</DOI><Authority>https://doi.org/</Authority></DOI><CollectionDataType>SCIENCE_QUALITY</CollectionDataType><RevisionDate>2021-05-19T10:06:11.467Z</RevisionDate><SuggestedUsage>To provide access to demographic data for the U.S.</SuggestedUsage><ProcessingLevelId>2</ProcessingLevelId><ArchiveCenter>SEDAC</ArchiveCenter><CollectionState>COMPLETE</CollectionState><RestrictionComment>None</RestrictionComment><UseConstraints><Description>This work is licensed under the Creative Commons Attribution 4.0 International License (https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0).
